title: Bug 121687Exception throws when export data in table which inside a grid cell.
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell.
EB: The data in the table inside the grid cell should be successfully exported without any exceptions being thrown.
SR: To reproduce: 1. Insert a table inside a grid cell. 2. Insert another table into another grid cell. 3. Try to export the data in the table inside the grid cell.
